scripts.up: php artisan serve&&sudo docker container start d_sql&&sudo docker container start d_redis&&php artisan queue:work
scripts.cls: php artisan config:clear&&php artisan cache:clear&&php artisan view:clear
scripts.docker_install: sudo docker pull mysql&&sudo docker run -p 3306:3306 -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=root -d --name=d_sql mysql&&sudo docker pull redis&&sudo docker run  -p 6379:6379 -d --name=d_redis redis
